  * [YOLO-NAS-m](https://github.com/ultralytics/assets/releases/download/v8.4.0/yolo_nas_m.pt)
  * [YOLO-NAS-l](https://github.com/ultralytics/assets/releases/download/v8.4.0/yolo_nas_l.pt)



